From MNR M OOSTHUYSEN Subject Re A KIND and LOVING God In article writes Leviticus And the daughter of any priest if she profane herself by playing the whore she profaneth her father she shall be burnt with Deuteronomy the tokens of virginity be not found for the damsel then they shall bring out the damsel to the door of her father's house and the men of the city shall stone her with stones that she Deuteronomy If a man be found lying with a woman married to a husband then they shall both of them Deuteronomy If a damsel that is a virgin be betrothed unto a husband and a man find her in the city and lie with her then ye shall bring them both out unto the gate of that city and ye shall stone them with stones that they Deuteronomy BUT if a man find a betrothed damsel in the field and the man force her and lie with her then the man only that lay with her shall IF it were'nt for the sin of men none of this killing would have been necesarry He is KIND and LOVING but also RIGHTEOUS SIN MUST BE Before Jesus man had to take the sins on But Jesus died and took it all upon Him so now we also have a FORGIVING If He were not KIND and LOVING there wouldn't have been any people